{"tid":1545104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"浸大學生會外務副會長入境澳洲時被扣查及翻查手機","createTime":"2019-09-05T20:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:24:35.000Z","uid":272355,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6e01421eaef0f33ad500cdb8f8804c8347afcb","tid":1545104,"uid":272355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:10:03.000Z","msg":"有冇澳洲巴絲知咩事?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學學生會外務副會長梁兆玉星期二到澳洲墨爾本機場入境時，被當地邊境人員拘留和查問半小時，期間被翻查手機。<br />\n<br />\n梁兆玉表示，她在入境時被兩名男邊境人員截停，帶到房間搜查，問她到澳洲的目的及有沒有帶攻擊性武器。邊境人員要求梁兆玉的手機解鎖，檢查相片及其他内容，一度將梁兆玉的手機帶離她的視線範圍。搜查期間，該兩名邊境人員形容香港的反修例示威為暴動。<br />\n<br />\n梁兆玉對此表示失望及難過，她相信是個別事件，兩名邊境人員可能是因自己的政治立場，或因她的學生領袖身份而有不禮貌舉動。<br />\n<br />\n梁兆玉因大專學界國際事務代表團的工作，到訪墨爾本。"},{"pid":"cbf7151c5594feb938e0130431a82043dffb63bd","tid":1545104,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:10:13.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"423aab9002c2c6775e96a0ed18bb0073001ef8cc","tid":1545104,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:12:18.000Z","msg":"香港警察老屈政治領袖係恐怖份子公佈各國"},{"pid":"2f074b45d45811af66568fda38690bb314e7bd31","tid":1545104,"uid":227174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:12:58.000Z","msg":"澳洲一早就淪陷咗, 呢兩年先開始立法限華以為來得切, 笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31093c377bb62e58b086a70f9f9b608a1258a1c","tid":1545104,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:13:41.000Z","msg":"人權呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌咩"},{"pid":"f6f11326d7f2aeb6855196838ac83af4d02ad978","tid":1545104,"uid":73509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:36:43.000Z","msg":"我識香港人30歲女，去左澳洲後藍到仆街，所以澳洲應該俾大陸統戰得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e4ce8f7a63da6c3b3d9eaa2fbd9ceeb4a01de4","tid":1545104,"uid":224541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"圍澳領?"},{"pid":"312a22c406081bccdc4e06818f76de0ce171ed06","tid":1545104,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"有冇梁兆玉ig?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}